node_modules/next/dist/docs/01-app/02-guides/upgrading/version-15.md:479:The `runtime` [segment configuration](/docs/app/api-reference/file-conventions/route-segment-config/runtime) previously supported a value of `experimental-edge` in addition to `edge`. Both configurations refer to the same thing, and to simplify the options, we will now error if `experimental-edge` is used. To fix this, update your `runtime` configuration to `edge`. A [codemod](/docs/app/guides/upgrading/codemods#app-dir-runtime-config-experimental-edge) is available to automatically do this.
